5264ee85506e64df41a92ac3.avif?t=1771014568 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >What does your future hold for you? Should you take advice from friends and family?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Are you a relationship guy who wants to hold out to meet someone special, or are you lonely and willing to just settle for your turn with someone to avoid being alone?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3247540/extras/de675c0d8d30afb33b5e2975bb350a75.avif?t=1771014568\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3247540/extras_big/de675c0d8d30afb33b5e2975bb350a75.avif?t=1771014568 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Maybe you are the type that prefers to avoid people or relationships altogether and instead be a man who goes his own way?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Going Your Own Way</i> pokes fun at the modern dating environment, relationships, and corporate workplace. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3247540/extras/66e47b39539f1cca50675f45d0815f81.avif?t=1771014568\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3247540/extras_big/66e47b39539f1cca50675f45d0815f81.avif?t=1771014568 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Do you lean blue-pill or red-pill?  Will your view of the real-world influence your decisions? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Going Your Own Way – Episode One</i> introduces the characters and lays the foundation for the story to come.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Episode One</strong> <strong>Features:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2,800+ images.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >24,000+ words.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Multiple decision paths that will influence future episodes. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Created using Ren'Py and Daz Studio.</p>",
